mission_executor  | ## Summary Report
mission_executor  | 
mission_executor  | ### The Candidate Pool
mission_executor  | There are **only 10 applicants**, so the "top 10" is the entire pool. All ten are strong candidates: CS degrees from solid universities (UCLA, UPenn, Michigan, UT Austin, UIUC, UW, Chicago, and strong state schools), 5–8 years of experience at reputable tech firms (Stripe, NVIDIA, Adobe, Dropbox, Oracle, Lyft, etc.), and relevant skills.
mission_executor  | 
mission_executor  | ### Ranking of All 10 Candidates (Fair, Merit-Based)
mission_executor  | 
mission_executor  | Based on depth of experience, seniority progression, skill breadth, and role relevance to software engineering:
mission_executor  | 
