mission_executor  | |------|-----------|---------------|
mission_executor  | | 1 | Michael Brown | 9 yrs exp, Intel → NVIDIA Lead, C++/Python/GPU programming — strong systems depth |
mission_executor  | | 2 | Sophia Miller | Square → Stripe Senior, Python/Java, financial systems (high-reliability domain) |
mission_executor  | | 3 | James Parker | Airbnb → Dropbox Lead, strong backend focus, 8 yrs experience |
mission_executor  | | 4 | Sarah Lee | IBM → Oracle Senior, Java/Python + database expertise, 7 yrs |
mission_executor  | | 5 | Olivia Taylor | Uber → Lyft Senior, Python/C++, mobile — broad skill set |
